Yang Haodong preached the spirit of the Sixth Plenary Session of the 19th CPC Central Committee and the Provincial Party Congress in Malanshan, drawing on the strength of the party 's century-old struggle history. Hunan Daily, December 10 th,(All-media reporter Gong Baiwei) According to the unified arrangement of the provincial party Committee, on the morning of December 10, Yang Haodong, member of the standing Committee of the provincial party Committee and minister of the propaganda department of the provincial party Committee, made an interactive speech in Malanshan Video Creation Park to thoroughly study and implement the spirit of the sixth plenary session of the 19th CPC Central Committee, study and implement the spirit of General Secretary Xi Jinping 's important instructions on Hunan' s important speech, and study and implement the spirit of the 12th provincial party congress. Yang Haodong from ideals and beliefs and initial mission, self-revolution and youth big party,The leaders of the Party and the Party 's theory and other three aspects, combined with their own feelings and personal experiences, explained the core meaning and practical requirements of the plenary spirit in a comprehensive and systematic way. He pointed out that the spirit of the plenary session should be combined with the spirit of General Secretary Xi Jinping' s important instructions and instructions on Hunan 's important speeches and the spirit of the provincial Party Congress, so as to strengthen the ideological, political and action consciousness of defending the "two establishments" and achieving the "two maintenances".Unswervingly follow the direction guided by General Secretary Xi Jinping. In the interactive exchange link, representatives of grass-roots cadres, enterprises and youth representatives asked questions about the relationship between the three historical resolutions, how to understand the decisive significance of the "Two Establishments", how to grasp the guidance of cultural enterprises, and how young people in the new era can draw strength from the century-old history of the Party. Yang Haodong answered them one by one in popular language and vivid examples. He sent a message to young Party members to learn from the Party's century-old struggle history. Draw forward strength and unite closely around the Party Central Committee.Unswervingly follow the Party and write responsibilities and responsibilities with youth dedication.
